OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772062277
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist spied on by MI5 and
OL,4,CPSNI should get damages, tribunal told
OL,6,FA former BBC journalist who had his
OL,7,Fphone data unlawfully obtained by MI5
OL,8,Fand the PSNI should be awarded
OL,9,F'substantial' damages, a specialist
OL,10,Ftribunal has been told.
OL,12,FPolice have admitted trying to track
OL,13,Fdown Vincent Kearney's sources over a
OL,14,Fperiod of years and creating a profile
OL,15,Fcontaining personal information on the
OL,16,Fbroadcaster's family.
OL,18,FMr Kearney, who now reports for RTE,
OL,19,Fwas in London on Wednesday for his
OL,20,Fcase against police and the security
OL,21,Fservices.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
