PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772062277
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist spied on by MI5 and
OL,4,CPSNI should get damages, tribunal told
OL,6,F"I was a target of a systematic, years-
OL,7,Flong campaign of illegal activity by
OL,8,Flaw enforcement agencies to access my
OL,9,Fjournalistic material.
OL,11,F"The scale of that material has been
OL,12,Fstaggering. MI5 have previously
OL,13,Fadmitted illegally accessing my
OL,14,Fcommunications data on two occasions.
OL,16,F"The PSNI have also conceded now (to)
OL,17,Faccessing my data illegally multiple
OL,18,Ftimes over multiple years.
OL,26,@xD@bpmxD@epn
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772062277
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist spied on by MI5 and
OL,4,CPSNI should get damages, tribunal told
OL,6,F"So, it is quite a staggering
OL,7,Fintrusion of privacy as well as my
OL,8,Fprofessional integrity and that has
OL,9,Fhad a really chilling impact on my
OL,10,Fability to conduct public service
OL,11,Fjournalism", Mr Kearney said.
OL,13,FThe BBC is jointly bringing the case
OL,14,Fbefore the Investigatory Powers
OL,15,FTribunal. It described the "extent and
OL,16,Feffect of unlawful interference" as "a
OL,17,Fmatter of serious concern".
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772062277
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist spied on by MI5 and
OL,4,CPSNI should get damages, tribunal told
OL,6,FThe tribunal heard the PSNI made a
OL,7,Fdetailed profile of Mr Kearney with
OL,8,Fthe aim of identifying sources for his
OL,9,Fstories.
OL,11,FHe is now seeking damages.
OL,13,F"They gathered material on who lives
OL,14,Fin our household. On my wife, on my
OL,15,Flate mother-in-law, on our children.
OL,17,F"Phone numbers, card details, car
OL,18,Fregistrations. So, that is a huge
OL,19,Fintrusion of privacy at a private
OL,20,Flevel as well.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772062277
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist spied on by MI5 and
OL,4,CPSNI should get damages, tribunal told
OL,6,F"Why gather that material? Why gather
OL,7,Finformation about card details and car
OL,8,Fregistrations unless you plan to at
OL,9,Fsome point conduct surveillance?", he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FIn 2025, the long-awaited McCullough
OL,13,Freview into the actions of the PSNI
OL,14,Fwas published.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
