PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772062277
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist spied on by MI5 and
OL,4,CPSNI should get damages, tribunal told
OL,6,FWhile the report did not find that
OL,7,Fpolice surveillance of journalists and
OL,8,Flawyers was widespread or systemic, it
OL,9,Frevealed 21 unlawful attempts were
OL,10,Fmade by police to track down the
OL,11,Fsources of 8 journalists in Northern
OL,12,FIreland.
OL,14,FAmong them UTV's Deborah McAleese and
OL,15,FSharon O'Neill.
OL,17,FIn a statement at the time, on behalf
OL,18,Fof UTV news, ITV said it was 'deeply
OL,19,Fconcerned' by the findings.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
