FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772062277
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist spied on by MI5 and
OL,4,CPSNI should get damages, tribunal told
OL,6,FThe National Union of Journalists
OL,7,F(NUJ) is calling for a wider
OL,8,Finvestigation.J"We are calling for
OL,9,Fthere to be a full public inquiry into
OL,10,Fsurveillance of journalists in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,F"That has to be what comes out of
OL,14,Fthis. We have to know the full extent
OL,15,Fof what has happened rather than these
OL,16,Fdrips and drops coming forward.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
