CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772062277
OL,3,CEx-BBC journalist spied on by MI5 and
OL,4,CPSNI should get damages, tribunal told
OL,6,F"It all needs to be exposed and clear.
OL,7,FThose who have perpetrated these
OL,8,Fthings need to be held accountable",
OL,9,FLaura Davison, NUJ General Secretary
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FThe PSNI said it would be
OL,13,Finappropriate to comment while legal
OL,14,Fproceedings are ongoing.
OL,16,FThis hearing is set to conclude on
OL,17,FThursday.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
